      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROSABELLE MARY (1) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and one placing from five starts. Comes off a (19.61) win last time, scoring by 6 lengths in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Expected to go close. KERT KERT (7) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Royal Bandit (20.25) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Leading player again. MELLCAT BAD BOY (4) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 4 lengths back in third (20.32) at this track in a Mix 2/3 over 350m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can feature again. JACOBITE THORN (2) has top-three aspirations after placing at big odds last time.",
